    <p class="has-gray-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.25rem;line-height:1.8">Born from a recognized need within New York's emerging cannabis industry, Buffalo Cannabis Network (BCN) is Western New York's premier professional association for cannabis businesses and industry professionals. Since our founding in 2022, we've provided the essential platform for collaboration, knowledge-sharing, and growth across the Buffalo region.</p>
