    <p class="has-gray-color has-text-color" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);font-size:1.25rem;line-height:1.8">Founded by Steve McMorrow and led by a board of dedicated local industry professionals, BCN connects cannabis entrepreneurs, dispensary owners, cultivators, medical marijuana professionals, and service providers throughout Western New York. We're committed to fostering an environment where every stakeholder has the opportunity to flourish in Buffalo's growing cannabis industry.</p>
